     </lcAnswerOption2>
     <lcAnswerOption2>
      <lcAnswerContent2>False</lcAnswerContent2>
      <lcCorrectResponse2/>
     </lcAnswerOption2>
    </lcAnswerOptionGroup2>
    <lcFeedbackIncorrect2>
      <p>No, look to the East.</p>
      <p>Because the Earth rotates from West to East,
